Comment 1: 
I've confirmed I can see the same thing with clang-3.5 on arm systems, however at that
stage of the build Go is not involved. 

This is a clang bug. If it reoccurs closer to the shipping date of clang 3.5 (middle of
the year, or later), please reopen the issue.
_Status changed to **WontFix**._
